org.cast.cwm.xml.transform
Class TransformChain

java.lang.Object
  org.cast.cwm.xml.transform.TransformChain
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDOMTransformer
public class TransformChain
extends Object
implements IDOMTransformer

A transform that is composed of a chain of other transformers. When applyTransform is called, it will run each of the sub-transforms in turn on the provided DOM.
